---
title: Iberian Chicken and Chickpea Bake with mushrooms and cherry tomatoes
description: The combination of chicken and chickpeas in a rich tomato sauce gives this recipe a distinctly Iberian air. In Spain, this dish might be referred to as a Cocido, but here it's merely called delicious. For best results, serve hot with a side of freshly warmed baguette.
